        "title": "How to set Finnish locale in java?",
        "body": "<p>Topic says it all.\nThe Locale.class seems to include some languages but I can't find Finnish among them.\n<strong>How do I get the finnish Locale?<\/strong> I need to set it as an argument to a method. Thank you.<\/p>\n\n<p>the method is as follows:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public String getMessage(String tag, Locale locale) { \n...\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
